    - target: {fileID: 6735205936001692925, guid: 1148a82719da0ba4f9dc7e58b85c2fae, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'The three main rooms have aberrations that sometimes spawn, these are
        "differences" in the world that happen over time

        When you see something
        that is possibly an aberration, you''ll need to first select the type of
        aberration you think it is.

        Once you''ve chosen which anomaly type
        you think it is, you left click on the spot where the anomaly is happening

        After
        a brief delay it''ll tell you whether you were right or wrong, and if you
        were right it''ll fix it for you.

        If it doesn''t work but you think
        it should''ve, you either missed the anomaly with your click, or you chose
        the wrong anomaly type and should try a different type.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6735205936001692925, guid: 1148a82719da0ba4f9dc7e58b85c2fae, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_fontSize
      value: 7.05
